data.description: Located in Far West SA, conveniently located just outside 1604 & 151, a short commute to SeaWorld, Hyatt Hill Country Resort, Six Flags, Lackland AFB and shopping. This stunning pre-owned LGI two story in sought after Luckey Ranch has 5 beds, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage has an open floor at entry, included is a gourmet kitchen which opens to the living room/dining area. The gourmet style kitchen has granite counters, subway tiled backsplash and stainless-steel appliances.  Right off the kitchen is the master bedroom which includes dual vanity bathroom and combo shower/tub with an adjacent x-tra large walk-in closet.  The second floor has a large game room/second living area and all four bedrooms, with hall entry bathroom and utility room.  For security conscious buyer(s), we have front and back cameras and a Ring doorbell.  The breathtaking backyard has lots of fruit trees, a new Purgola and is perfect for entertaining or just relaxing after a long day. Come see this one today!  **Open House Saturday, 11/04, 12-2**
